--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.2.0 (2020-02-01)
F: Add support for CentOS 8

* Version 2.1.1 (2020-01-08)
B: Minor Jinja2 statement fix

* Version 2.1.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 2.0.0 (2019-02-02)
C: Redesign 'monit_config_all' option (alter config variable to string)
C: Redesign 'monit_config_group' option (alter config variable to string)
C: Redesign 'monit_config_host' option (alter config variable to string)

* Version 1.0.1 (2018-12-13)
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-13)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'

* Version 0.3.1 (2018-12-10)
B: Fix Jinja2 templating typo

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-12-10)
F: Extend 'monit_mail_server' parameter

* Version 0.2.3 (2018-12-07)
E: Minor 'monit_mail_subject' improvement

* Version 0.2.2 (2018-12-07)
E: Remove operating system information from alert message

* Version 0.2.1 (2018-12-06)
E: Remove email information from alert message

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-12-06)
E: Improve 'monit_mail_server' parameter
E: Redesign 'monit_mail_to' parameter
E: Extend 'monit_web_server_allow' parameter
E: Remove 'monit_mail_exclusions' parameter
E: Remove kernel information from alert message

* Version 0.1.2 (2018-12-05)
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-12-03)
B: Fix template source

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-12-03)
F: Initial release
